5. 安全提示 / Security Notice
   代码经过安全审计但仍存在未修复的协议级安全洞 (详见 SECURITY_AUDIT.md).
   即使仅用于学习, 也不建议在生产网络中暴露监听端口. 如需测试, 请使用
   本地回环 (127.0.0.1) 或受控的隔离环境.

   The code has been security-audited but unresolved protocol-level
   vulnerabilities remain (see SECURITY_AUDIT.md). Even for learning
   purposes, do not expose listening ports in production networks. Use
   loopback (127.0.0.1) or controlled isolated environments for testing.
